  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad peegahje Juhda pee muhfu masakajs Brahlis pee\na/ un fazzija: Ak mans Kungs!\nai taws Kalps/ luhdsans/ kahdu\nWahrdü preeksch manna Kunga\nAufim runna/ un ne apskaisfees\npahr tawu Kalpu/ jo tu effi tik\nugsts/ ka Warais.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mans Kungs waizaja\nawus Kalpus/ un fazzija: Ir-\nag jums Tehwa/ jeb Brahta?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzijam mehs us\nmannu Kungu: Mums irr weens\npezzi Tehws/ un weens Behrns/\nas tam Wezzuma dsumnis/ tas\nasakajs/ un winna Brahlis\nr nomirris/ un tas irr weens\nats no fawas Mahtes atlizzis/\nn winna Tehws mihle winzu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazziji tu us taweem\nalpeem: Weddeet to pee man\nja/ es winnu schehlofschu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzijam mehs us\nmannu Kungu: Tas Behrns ne\narr fawu Tehwu atstaht/ ja tas\niwu Tehwu painett/ tad winsch\nomirs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazziji tu us taweem\nalpeem: Ja juhfu masakajs\nBrahlis ar jums ne nahks sem-\nê/ tad juhs mannu Waigu\npairs ne redsefeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad mehs pee tawu\nKalpu mannu Tehwu nahzam/\nn mehs winnam pafazzijam\nmanna Kunga Wahrdus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija muhfu Tehws:\nNo-eita attak/ pirzeet nuuns Eh-\ndeena kahdu Maggumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzijam mehs:\nMehs ne twarram leja no-eet: Ja\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "masakajs Brahlis pee\nmums ne irr/ tad mehs no-eestun:\nJo mehs ne warram ta Wihra\nWaigu redseht/ ja fchis muhfu\nmasakajs Brahlis ar mums\nne irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija taws Kalps/\nmans Tehws us mums/ juhs sin-\nnat/ ka manna Seewa man di-\nwi irr dsemdejsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas weens irr no man-\nnim tsgahjis/ un es efinu fazzijis/\ntas irr tihri faplohsfhts/ un es to\nne efinutamehr redsejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tad juhs arridsan scho\nno mannahm Azzim noxemfeet/\nun tam kahda Liksta usees/ tad\njuhs mannu firmus Mattus/\nar Sird-Ehsteem Rappa nowed-\ndiseet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nu tad/ kad es pee tawu\nKalpu mannu Tehwu nahkfchu/\nun tas Puifs ar mums ne irr/\njo winna Dwehfele ta pascha\nDwehfelei peelihp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tas notiks/ kad tas\nto Puifi ne redsehs klaht effam/\ntad tas nomirs/ un tawi Kalpi\nnoweddihs tawa Kalpa/ manna\nTehwa/firmus Mattus ar Sird-\nEhsteem Rappa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo taws Kalps irr gat-\nwojis/ preekich to Puifi/ pee ta-\nwu Tehwu/ un fazzijis/ ja ee\nwinzu tew atpakak ne atived-\ndischu/ tad gribbu es pee manna\nTehwa fawu Muhscbu nosee-\ndsfs buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu laid jelle taw\nKalps/ ta Puicha Weeta pa\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
